Step.SQLStatement: INSERT INTO AD_EMailConfig(AD_Client_ID, AD_Org_ID, IsActive, Created, CreatedBy, Updated, UpdatedBy, AD_EMailConfig_ID, Port, SMTPHost, IsSmtpAuthorization, EncryptionType, AuthMechanism, Name, Protocol) SELECT c.AD_Client_ID, 0, 'Y', getDate(), 100, getDate(), 100, nextidfunc(54297, 'Y'), CASE WHEN c.SMTPHost = 'mail.smtp.port' THEN 587 ELSE 25 END, c.SMTPHost, c.IsSmtpAuthorization, CASE WHEN c.SMTPHost = 'mail.smtp.port' THEN 'T' ELSE 'N' END, 'L', c.Name || ' ' || c.SMTPHost, CASE WHEN c.SMTPHost = 'mail.smtp.port' THEN 'I' ELSE 'S' END FROM AD_Client c WHERE c.SMTPHost IS NOT NULL;
Step.RollbackStatement: DELETE FROM AD_EMailConfig WHERE EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM AD_Client c WHERE c.AD_Client_ID = AD_EMailConfig.AD_Client_ID AND c.SMTPHost = AD_EMailConfig.SMTPHost)

Step.SQLStatement: UPDATE AD_Client SET AD_EMailConfig_ID = (SELECT MAX(ec.AD_EMailConfig_ID) FROM AD_EMailConfig ec WHERE ec.AD_Client_ID = AD_Client.AD_Client_ID AND ec.SMTPHost = AD_Client.SMTPHost)
Step.RollbackStatement: UPDATE AD_Client SET AD_EMailConfig_ID = NULL WHERE EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM AD_EMailConfig ec WHERE ec.AD_Client_ID = AD_Client.AD_Client_ID AND ec.SMTPHost = AD_Client.SMTPHost)
